    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black Metallic. This example features the legendary S54B32 naturally aspirated straight-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure Double VANOS. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M Variable Differential Lock. Mechanically flawless, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed for preventative longevity. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the interior retains its factory matte finish and Nappa leather integrity. A true collector\u2019s specimen with a documented service history and zero deferred maintenance.",
