    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly pristine 2021 Luxury Sport Sedan that defines the term 'mint condition.' This vehicle has been meticulously garage-kept and climate-controlled since day one. The exterior features a flawless factory paint finish, recently treated with a multi-stage ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like shine with zero swirl marks, chips, or imperfections. Step inside to an interior that still retains that new-car aroma; the premium hand-stitched leather seats show absolutely no signs of wear, bolsters are firm, and the dashboard is free of any UV fading. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a full documented service history from the authorized dealership and only 8,500 original miles. All systems\u2014from the advanced infotainment to the adaptive suspension\u2014function perfectly. This sale includes both original key fobs, all owner\u2019s manuals, and a custom-fitted car cover. This is a rare opportunity to own a showroom-quality vehicle without the new-car depreciation.",
      "price": 44500.0,
