    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? This car is in absolute mint condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken incredible care of it, and it\u2019s been pampered every single mile. It\u2019s a total dream to drive and looks stunning from every angle. I\u2019m looking for someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come say hi and take a look for yourself\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 43900.0,
