    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable 997.2 Carrera S, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six engine paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. This specimen boasts a documented service history and meticulous PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) calibration. Every mechanical component, from the four-piston monobloc calipers to the limited-slip differential, remains in factory-spec, concours condition. This is a collector-grade example for the discerning purist, offering surgical throttle response and a pristine undercarriage with zero signs of thermal cycling wear or fluid seepage.",
